data.description: Come and see this spacious 5-bedroom/ 3bath. All rooms have laminate flooring and tile in the bathrooms. The kitchen has stainless steel appliances, cabinets are all wood with brushed handles and all the drawers are soft-close, and big farmbarn sink. The kitchen has plenty of space for a formal dining area and is right next to the family room, which makes the home great for entertaining! All bathrooms have been up dated, completely update 4 years ago. The back and side yard are large and have plenty of space all fenced in. Call now to set up your showing today!
